<ul dir="auto">
<li>Uses a <strong>honeycomb hex grid</strong> arranged on a circular disc platform.</li>
<li>Rows alternate between <strong>3, 6, 7, 8, 7, 8, 7, 3 effective positions</strong> to create the staggered structure.</li>
<li><code>enter</code> and <code>space</code> are <strong>rounded pill keys</strong>, not hexagons.</li>
<li>Numbers and symbols occupy the outer columns of the layout.</li>
<li>The Shift layer replaces outer-column numbers with punctuation: <code>! @ # $ % ^ &amp; * ( )</code>.</li>
<li>Default legends should display in <strong>lowercase</strong>, unless <strong>Shift</strong> is held.</li>
</ul>
